  (descr "Eurorack faceplate light pipe for a 0603 LED on a behind-panel PCB. No Edge.Cuts hole — leaves the FR4 solid and translucent. Soldermask is removed on both sides so bare FR4 transmits the LED light. 2.5 mm window diameter.")
